sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Mgr as PPC Manager
    participant Sheet as Budget Sheet
    participant Bot as Budget Updater<br/>(runs daily, 8:15 AM)
    participant Ads as Google Ads API
    participant Slack as Slack

    Mgr->>Sheet: Enter changes — account, shared budget, new amount
    Note over Mgr,Sheet: A human decides every dollar amount.<br/>The automation never invents one.

    Bot->>Sheet: Read rows not yet marked done
    loop Each pending row
        Bot->>Bot: Validate — amount must be over $0
        Bot->>Ads: Update the budget amount — that one field, nothing else
        Ads-->>Bot: Confirmed (or error)
    end
    Bot->>Sheet: Mark successes done ✓ (one batch write)

    opt Any row failed
        Bot->>Slack: One consolidated alert — what failed and why,<br/>plus what succeeded
        Note over Sheet,Slack: Failed rows stay unmarked —<br/>the sheet itself is the retry queue.<br/>Tomorrow's run picks them up automatically.
        Mgr->>Sheet: Fix the data — no code, no redeploy
    end
